 de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique]]|language=French|accessdate=April 6, 2020}}</ref> || 10 || 5<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://topplista.no/charts/singles/2020-w11/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 11, 2020|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=March 14, 2020}}</ref> || \u2014 || 35 || 8 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a|Non-album singles}}<ref name=\"MTV\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Alone, Pt. II]]\"<br>{{small|(with [[Alan Walker (music producer)|Alan Walker]])}}\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 68 || 47 || 4 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Alone, Pt. II\" did not enter the NZ Top 40 Singles Chart, but peaked at number 26 on the NZ Hot Singles Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4800|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=January 6, 2020|accessdate=January 4, 2020}}</ref>}} || 25 || 47 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Kings & Queens (Ava Max song)|Kings & Queens]]\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.avamax.com/kingsandqueens/|title=Ava Max {{!}} Kings & Queens Available 3.13 {{!}} RSVP NOW|website=avamax.com|access-date=March 5, 2020}}</ref>\n| 2020\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 197<br /><ref name=\"FRA Week 12\"/> || 52 || 9<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2020-14/|title=Topp 20 Single 2020-14|website=VG-lista 2020|language=nb-NO|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>|| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Kings & Queens\" did not enter the NZ Top 40 Singles Chart, but peaked at number 20 on the NZ Hot Singles Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4836|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=March 23, 2020|accessdate=March 21, 2020}}</ref>}} || 30<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sverigetopplistan.se/chart/41?dspy=2020&dspp=13|title=Veckolista Singlar, vecka 13|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref> || 22 || 71\n|\n| {{TBA}}\n|-<!-- Please do not add Blood Sweat & Tears, Freaking Me Ou